{"tid":441512,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇R 高手","createTime":"2017-10-19T17:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T00:14:49.000Z","uid":45177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d23e86131946ac3ed7215a833815f9b655b23ecc","tid":441512,"uid":45177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;A&nbsp;twin&nbsp;prime&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;pair&nbsp;of&nbsp;primes&nbsp;(x,&nbsp;y),&nbsp;such&nbsp;that&nbsp;y&nbsp;=&nbsp;x&nbsp;+&nbsp;2.&nbsp;Construct&nbsp;a&nbsp;list&nbsp;of&nbsp;all&nbsp;twin&nbsp;primes&nbsp;<br />\nless&nbsp;than&nbsp;1000.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9060abde1eac83a443f3d0085fd70c1f0df6c71","tid":441512,"uid":45177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A twin prime is a pair of primes (x, y), such that y = x + 2. Construct a list of all twin primes less than 1000.<br />\n<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2271accffffd322c8a005d2352d2a9dd637dbd2b","tid":441512,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"1000 * 2.14 = 2400"},{"pid":"01fa4145ee57231ae748f6a2d1d22e9d1ec0fa48","tid":441512,"uid":107620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T00:12:41.000Z","msg":"用python寫:<br />\n<br />\ndef isPrime(num):<br />\n    if num&lt;2:<br />\n        return False <br />\n    for i in range(2,num):<br />\n        if num%i==0:<br />\n            return False <br />\n    return True <br />\n<br />\nans=[]<br />\nfor i in range (1001):<br />\n    if isPrime (i) and isPrime (i+2):<br />\n        ans.append ([i,i+2])<br />\n<br />\nprint (ans)<br />\n<br />\n利申未用過R<br />\n但你明咗個logic就得<br />\n用咩language寫都差唔多"},{"pid":"caa13928e543bebc7dd1bbcd4f0c8d1dca3113cc","tid":441512,"uid":107620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T00:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用python寫:<br />\n<br />\ndef isPrime(num):<br />\n    if num&lt;2:<br />\n        return False <br />\n    for i in range(2,num):<br />\n        if num%i==0:<br />\n            return False <br />\n    return True <br />\n<br />\nans=[]<br />\nfor i in range (1001):<br />\n    if isPrime (i) and isPrime (i+2):<br />\n        ans.append ([i,i+2])<br />\n<br />\nprint (ans)<br />\n<br />\n利申未用過R<br />\n但你明咗個logic就得<br />\n用咩language寫都差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q7iwk6uv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq7iwk6uv&h=33c4d5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回覆出到嚟冇哂格式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}